02199e1aafd1591ebb1838bf8e74457d","tid":478762,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"小型公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 住親都cheap野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫做唔洗日日坐係度有得走下，又可以忙裡偷閒"},{"pid":"5404f8a63b6ac335dae1b0e6ca4af7aad2195dbc","tid":478762,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"出trip次次都要做陪客食飯飲酒<br />\n邊有時間叫雞"},{"pid":"505341b62ada394490dbfbe28fa8b7011bc8d0a5","tid":478762,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想返啲有得公幹既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要出trip 既人會同你講冇咩必要都唔好做空中飛人<br />\n公幹其實並唔好玩<br />\n仲好撚鳩柒麻煩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">俾我番香港office番工啦仆街</span>"},{"pid":"6f68b336f3a274c885821b5e135f091ae3b645d8","tid":478762,"uid":24296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"係大公司做disbursement <br />\n成日見啲claim form  幾萬幾萬咁黎<br />\n我都想呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813bf86811a37acd8ad1185288b826553b49a48b","tid":478762,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時出trip住五星級，最初一兩次好滾動，之後已經好公式化，做野,健身，食酒店野 健身，都好似無咩特別，聽過有啲人會叫女女上房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享下</blockquote><br />\n你似做飛鴨喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa83dec71160b7f94b628f6775bc0c134854bb3","tid":478762,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"公司比哂就係<br />\n<br />\n有d係admin負責book機票住宅<br />\n<br />\n佢地有平book平, 另外食飯都未必實報實銷, 低位每日得HKD200津貼"},{"pid":"c7a7597d96b7a9d337da7fc1a95c50e0d5b53314","tid":478762,"uid":5008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司比哂就係<br />\n<br />\n有d係admin負責book機票住宅<br />\n<br />\n佢地有平book平, 另外食飯都未必實報實銷, 低位每日得HKD200津貼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真 果2 3舊水一日係歐洲夠食條毛咩 如果酒店包早餐仲要扣你4份1 計到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6440f69e7a44d63f12a08159fd24c42d0244ab","tid":478762,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"公司full paid呢？"},{"pid":"de8e5563e7d8874295487022ecb066d498e3420e","tid":478762,"uid":42823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"出trip其實唔過引，好多野都突發，要走之前攪掂有時都幾大壓力，雖然可以extend，但比人感覺唔多好<br />\n但勝在可以周圍行下，又可以stay behind，慳返機票酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 平均個幾月飛一次"}]}